hopobject.body: The manager prostate eze max uk It's doubtful that Samsung will get similar treatment, because the two cases are fundamentally different, says intellectual property consultant Florian Mueller. And even though the ban is focused on older Samsung products, it could also apply to its most popular current products, "if those infringe these patents in the same way older devices did," Mueller says. "Samsung can avoid infringement with workarounds blessed by the ITC, but it's not known yet how good those alternative techniques are."
